# processor

## API

### ```GET: /results?offset=0``` 

Returns a list of hits. Offset, if set, determines how many entries are skipped.

```json
[
    {
        "coordinates": {
            "x": 500,
            "y": 5000
        },
        "time": "29/11/24 11:13:21.080171",
        "image": "",
        "distance": 5.0,
        "detected": []
    }]
```



### ```POST: /img``` 

example post data:

```json
{
        "coordinates": {
            "x": 500,
            "y": 5000
        },
        "time": "29/11/24 11:13:21.080171",
        "image": "",
        "distance": 5
}
```
